4175 void CreatureObjectImplementation::readObject(ObjectInputStream* stream) {
4176  uint16 _varCount = stream->readShort();
4177  for (int i = 0; i < _varCount; ++i) {
4178  uint32 _nameHashCode;
4179  TypeInfo<uint32>::parseFromBinaryStream(&_nameHashCode, stream);
4180 
4181  uint32 _varSize = stream->readInt();
4182 
4183  int _currentOffset = stream->getOffset();
4184 
4185  if(CreatureObjectImplementation::readObjectMember(stream, _nameHashCode)) {
4186  }
4187 
4188  stream->setOffset(_currentOffset + _varSize);
4189  }
4190 
4191  initializeTransientMembers();
4192 }

5843 
5844 CreatureObjectAdapter::CreatureObjectAdapter(CreatureObject* obj) : TangibleObjectAdapter(obj) {
5845 }
5846 
5847 void CreatureObjectAdapter::invokeMethod(uint32 methid, DistributedMethod* inv) {
5848  DOBMessage* resp = inv->getInvocationMessage();
5849 
5850  switch (methid) {
5851  case RPC_INITIALIZEMEMBERS__:
5852  {
5853  initializeMembers();
5854  }
5855  break;
5856  case RPC_FINALIZE__:
5857  {
5858  finalize();
5859  }
5860  break;
5861  case RPC_CREATECHILDOBJECTS__:
5862  {
5863  createChildObjects();
5864  }
5865  break;
5866  case RPC_INITIALIZETRANSIENTMEMBERS__:
5867  {
5868  initializeTransientMembers();
5869  }
5870  break;
5871  case RPC_CLEARQUEUEACTION__INT_FLOAT_INT_INT_:
5872  {
5873  clearQueueAction(inv->getUnsignedIntParameter(), inv->getFloatParameter(), inv->getUnsignedIntParameter(), inv->getUnsignedIntParameter());
